{
  "title": "What’s Next for Insurance Regulation?",
  "body": "<html><body><div class=\"node__content\"> <section class=\"detail-page-head full-width-block\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-12\"> <small>IASA- <span class=\"field field--name-created field--type-created field--label-hidden\"><time class=\"datetime\" datetime=\"2026-02-24T13:38:05+00:00\" title=\"Tuesday, February 24, 2026 - 13:38\">Tue, 02/24/2026 - 13:38</time></span></small><h1><span class=\"field field--name-title field--type-string field--label-hidden\">What’s Next for Insurance Regulation?</span></h1></div></div></div> </section> <section class=\"detail-page additional-height\"><div class=\"container medium\"><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-8-lg\"><div class=\"feature-image-visability\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-banner field--type-entity-reference field--label-hidden field__item\"><article class=\"media media--type-image media--view-mode-default insurance-library-image\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-media-image field--type-image field--label-visually_hidden\"><div class=\"field__label visually-hidden\">Image</div><div class=\"field__item\"> <img alt=\"What’s Next for Insurance Regulation header image\" class=\"lazyload img-fluid\" data-src=\"/sites/default/files/2026-02/Double%20Guest%20Template.png\" height=\"844\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2026-02/Double%20Guest%20Template.png\" width=\"2008\"/></div></div> </article></div></div><div class=\"audio-player\"></div><p><em>InsuranceAUM is pleased to share this special edition of Insurance Insights, a co-branded conversation presented by </em><a href=\"https://www.griffithfoundation.org/\"><em>The Institutes Griffith Foundation</em></a><em> and </em><a href=\"https://www.iasa.org/\"><em>IASA</em></a><em>, affiliates of The Institutes.</em></p><p>In this interview, the Honorable Scott A. White, Virginia Insurance Commissioner and President of the National Association of Insurance Commissioners (NAIC), offers candid insights into the evolving regulatory landscape, the key industry challenges faced in 2025, and emerging priorities for 2026. The discussion also explores how the NAIC operates within America’s state-based regulatory system to support a resilient insurance marketplace.</p><p></p><p><br/> </p><div class=\"avalible-pods\"><div class=\"block block-block-content block-block-content9a03abe3-6e62-4857-9ccf-a8978d7294f7\" id=\"block-podcastisavailableon\"><div class=\"field field--name-field-link-with-image field--type-entity-reference-revisions field--label-hidden field__items\"><div class=\"field__item\"><h3>The InsuranceAUM.com podcast is available on</h3><div class=\"btns-wrapper\"> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://open.spotify.com/show/6WIbsYrL1BXuJMPsZXSk8R\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn2.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/insuranceaum-com/id1500643401\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2023-08/btn3.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://www.amazon.com/InsuranceAUM-com/dp/B08K57V1D6\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-03/Frame%20366%20%281%29.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a> <a aria-label=\"extrerbal-link\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@InsuranceAUMCommunity\" target=\"_blank\"> <img alt=\"\" height=\"52px\" src=\"/sites/default/files/2025-03/frame_366%20%281%29%20%281%29.png\" width=\"200px\"/></a></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"col-4-lg\"><div class=\"addtoany-social-icons mb-3\"><div class=\"addtoany-social-icons mb-3\"><h4>Share this post</h4> <span class=\"a2a_kit a2a_kit_size_32 addtoany_list d-flex gap-2 justify-content-start\" data-a2a-title=\"What’s Next for Insurance Regulation?\" data-a2a-url=\"https://insuranceaum.com/whats-next-for-insurance-regulation\"><a class=\"a2a_button_linkedi